BergLeaderM			~kKing Aaron Leone sighs, "One day I may leave this world without an heir, for my beloved wife can no longer bear children. If only Jala could grant us a miracle."
BergLeaderM			~kKing Aaron Leone smiles warmly, "Though I have no son to inherit my throne, my beloved wife and I have been blessed with three wonderful daughters."
BergLeaderM			~kKing Aaron Leone looks sad and says, "My advisors have urged me to father a bastard, but they do not understand how deeply I love my wife.  I could never betray her."
BergLeaderM			~kKing Aaron Leone says, "For the safety of Berg and its inhabitants!  Always remember that when you leave our gates to fight the monsters that threaten our city."
BergLeaderM			~kKing Aaron Leone speaks softly, "There is much that troubles me.  Sometimes I wish I had someone to confide in. Perhaps you would listen?"
