JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "Music can affect you in so many ways.  A song can change your mood, even your whole day."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "Golems are animated servants, neither alive nor dead.  They are powerful tools of Jala."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "Those who have passed can still hear our songs. Remember to honor them with a gentle tune."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "A prism is a handy tool.  You never know where it might come in handy."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "A great song is one that endures, even when I'm not around."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "Music gives us memories.  The longer a melody has existed, the more memories it holds."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "If our king loves music, then there is little wrong in the land."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "I don't think good and evil are opposites.  Anything done for love goes beyond both."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "Music never lies - it makes you feel something.  A song lets you feel a thought."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "So vast is art, so narrow is the human wit."
JalaPriestess			~kPriestess Themala says, "True ease in lyrics comes from art, not chance.  Those who have learned to dance move most gracefully."
